1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,140
Recently, someone in my family was scammed.

2
00:00:03,660 --> 00:00:06,820
The message looked real.
The threat felt urgent.

3
00:00:07,720 --> 00:00:10,140
And in that moment,
they didn't know who to ask.

4
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:14,180
That uncertainty is where
many scams win.

5
00:00:14,480 --> 00:00:18,200
Not because people are careless,
but because the message creates fear

6
00:00:18,660 --> 00:00:21,760
and demands a decision
before there is time to think.

7
00:00:22,940 --> 00:00:26,100
I built a web app called Pausa
for that moment:

8
00:00:26,680 --> 00:00:30,100
a calm place to stop and ask,
"Is this real?"

9
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:32,220
"And what should I do next?"

10
00:00:33,400 --> 00:00:37,600
It should feel like having a security-savvy
person in your family right there with you.

11
00:00:39,040 --> 00:00:43,720
Because not everyone is digitally native,
Pausa lets you speak, take a photo,

12
00:00:43,940 --> 00:00:46,340
choose a screenshot,
or paste the message.

13
00:00:47,020 --> 00:00:51,940
It works on phone, tablet, and web,
and can be installed in a few taps.

14
00:00:53,600 --> 00:00:55,260
Here's the actual product.

15
00:00:56,160 --> 00:00:58,680
I talk to it about a bank alert.

16
00:00:59,240 --> 00:01:04,580
Pausa checks it and explains
why it may be dangerous,

17
00:01:05,380 --> 00:01:08,520
then gives you the next steps.

18
00:01:09,860 --> 00:01:13,080
Using the intelligence of GPT-5.6,

19
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:17,380
it identifies and explains
the signs it can observe,

20
00:01:17,380 --> 00:01:20,020
such as pressure, fear, and urgency,

21
00:01:20,220 --> 00:01:25,980
then guides the person away from that
suspicious message toward a trusted channel.

22
00:01:26,600 --> 00:01:31,500
I built this app using my voice,
describing the problem to Codex,

23
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:36,720
iterating through the experience,
and testing the safety behavior.

24
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:41,980
Codex turned that conversation
into a working bilingual application,

25
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:47,060
while GPT-5.6 provides
the reasoning and vision.

26
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:51,100
Pausa passed all safety evaluations.

27
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:55,820
Pausa is designed to help families
slow down and feel less alone,

28
00:01:56,040 --> 00:02:00,100
and take one calmer,
safer next step.

29
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:04,600
Try it out now for free
and keep your people safe.
